Let's try some plotly

```{r, message=FALSE, warning=FALSE}
library(widgetframe)
library(dplyr)
library(ggplot2)
library(plotly)
library(webshot)

p1 <- mtcars %>%
 mutate(Cylinders = as.factor(cyl)) %>%
 ggplot(., aes(x=hp, y=mpg, col=Cylinders) ) + 
  geom_point(size=4, alpha=0.7) + 
  theme_bw()
```

```{r}
p2 <- ggplotly(p1)
frameWidget(p2)
```